  "detailed_description": "The Crazy Chicken first saw the light of day in 1999, and has been on lots of adventures since then. Now it's back to face its biggest challenge yet: In Crazy Chicken: Tiger & Chicken, you play the hero in a fast-paced story filled with terrifying enemies and dramatic combat. As a Shaolin fighter, you must liberate your oppressed people and save the love of your life.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Action RPG for the whole family<br></li><li>Fight with a variety of weapons<br></li><li>Sophisticated skill system<br></li><li>Beautiful 3D graphics<br></li><li>Supports controllers</li></ul>",
